考試日期（年月日）︰2015/3/3
考試時限（分鐘）：30分鐘左右(最後一節課)

試題 :

Student ID: ______              Name: ______

s = ___ = 12 －“the last digit of your ID”,  3 ≦ s ≦ 12

                            *
1) Consider the group G = (Z  , ×mod 17)
                            17

       -1
   a) s  (the multiplicative inverse of s) is ___

   b) o(s) (the order of s) = ___

   c) The index  [G : < s >] = ___

   d) Explain why  G  is a cyclic group


                                                      *
2) Consider the homomorphism  f:(Z  , ＋ mod 16) → (Z  , ×mod 17) defined by
                                  16                  17

   f(1) = s

   a) f(0) = ___      b) f(2) = ___    c) Is f an isomorphism?  Explain


3) |GL (Z  )| = ____,    |SL (Z  )| = ____
      2  17                 2  17


